We will write a Python script to sort these words alphabetically.

```python
# List of words to be sorted
words = [
    "admixture", "catwalk", "shelve", "panamanian", "reluctant", 
    "higgins", "suction", "irremediable", "chateaux", "offertory", 
    "malthusian", "coordinate", "tunis", "pecos", "equine"
]

# Sorting the list alphabetically
sorted_words = sorted(words)

# Printing the sorted list
print(sorted_words)
```
